Name:               Regex-NFA
Version:            0.1
Synopsis:           NFA-based regular expression engine
Homepage:           https://github.com/awagner83/haskell-regex-nfa
License:            BSD3
License-file:       LICENSE
Author:             Adam Wagner
Maintainer:         awagner83@gmail.com
Category:           Text
Build-type:         Simple
Cabal-version:      >=1.8

Library
  Exposed-modules:  Data.Match
                    Data.NFA
                    Text.Regex.NFA.Compiler
  Hs-Source-Dirs:   src
  GHC-Options:      -Wall -O2
  Build-depends:    base, parsec >= 3.1.1, mtl >= 2
  
Test-Suite test
  Type:             exitcode-stdio-1.0
  Hs-Source-Dirs:   tests
  GHC-Options:      -Wall
  Main-is:          Main.hs
  Build-depends:    base, Regex-NFA

